OL,3,C'I'm so happy to be back': Richard
OL,4,CAshcroft on homecoming gig
OL,6,FMusician Richard Ashcroft has hailed
OL,7,Ftwo gigs in his hometown as "some of
OL,8,Fthe greatest two days in his musical
OL,9,Fcareer".
OL,11,FThe former frontman of The Verve
OL,12,Fplayed his first gig in Wigan for more
OL,13,Fthan 25 years, singing in front of two
OL,14,Fsellout crowds at the town's Robin
OL,15,FPark Arena.
OL,17,FWhen tickets went on sale for the
OL,18,Fhomecoming gig on Saturday 20 July
OL,19,Fthey sold out in less than 24 hours,
OL,20,Fprompting another to be added to the
OL,21,Fcalendar the following night.
