OL,3,C'I'm so happy to be back': Richard
OL,4,CAshcroft on homecoming gig
OL,6,FAshcroft, who formed band The Verve in
OL,7,F1989, says he has been trying to get
OL,8,Fback to Wigan for years after playing
OL,9,Fan iconic gig with his former band at
OL,10,FHaigh Hall in May 1998.
OL,12,FMore than 13,000 people packed into
OL,13,Fthe area on Saturday night where,
OL,14,Fdespite the rain, following support
OL,15,Facts Maxwell Varey and Liverpool band
OL,16,FRed Rum Club and Cast, he took to the
OL,17,Fstage.
