OL,3,C'I'm so happy to be back': Richard
OL,4,CAshcroft on homecoming gig
OL,6,FHe walked on to screens showing a
OL,7,Fmontage of Wigan landmarks, ensuring
OL,8,Fthe crowd was in no doubt of
OL,9,FAshcroft's roots.
OL,11,FWearing a sparkly jacket and jeans,
OL,12,Fhis said: "For anyone not from Wigan,
OL,13,Fthis is authentic experience. Dig it".
OL,15,FAshcroft told crowds on Sunday: "These
OL,16,Ftwo days have been some of the
OL,17,Fgreatest of my musical career, I am so
OL,18,Fhappy to be back home.
