OL,3,C'I'm so happy to be back': Richard
OL,4,CAshcroft on homecoming gig
OL,6,F"This has shown that this town can put
OL,7,Fon amazing music events, and long may
OL,8,Fit continue, and whether it be next
OL,9,Fyear or the year after, I think I need
OL,10,Fto be in that stadium over there,
OL,11,Fdon't you?"
OL,13,FThroughout both gigs he made numerous
OL,14,Freferences to his roots, including
OL,15,Fspeaking of his memories growing up,
OL,16,Fabout local Billinge Hospital and his
OL,17,Fold school Upholland High.
