OL,3,C'I'm so happy to be back': Richard
OL,4,CAshcroft on homecoming gig
OL,6,FHe also mentioned the bitter rivalry
OL,7,Fbetween Rugby League rivals Wigan
OL,8,FWarriors and St Helens, the Bees Knees
OL,9,Fand infamous Wigan restaurant Santi
OL,10,FBag.
OL,12,FHis reference to playing the Brick
OL,13,FCommunity stadium, home of Wigan
OL,14,FAthletic and Wigan Warriors, was
OL,15,Fgreeted by rapturous cheers from the
OL,16,Fcrowd.
